text: Claudia Christian (born Claudia Ann Coghlan on August 10, 1965) is an American actress, singer, author, musician, and activist. She is known for her role as Commander Susan Ivanova on Babylon 5, as Captain Maynard on Fox's 9-1-1, and as the voice of Hera on the Netflix series Blood of Zeus.According to the State of California.
